          <p class="text-white mt-4">Centre for Entrepreneurship Development (CED). Anna University is carrying out various programs for kindling the entrepreneurship inspirations of the Engineering College students of Tamil Nadu State.

Centre for Entrepreneurship Development (CED) , Anna University has established a dedicated MAKERS LAB under the funding scheme of RUSA 2.0 to support and promote innovations and to translate ideas into prototype or products.

The objective of CED Makers lab is to provide support for students and faculties of University Campus, Anna University to convert their startup idea into prototype.</p>
        
        
  
  
  
  
